Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3d_m = 0 then end if not (gs_shadow) then shadow off
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then resol 3 else resol gs_resol endif
pen gs_cont_pen material gs_seat_mat boardThk = 0.02
unID=1
hotspot a/2,0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2,b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2,0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2,b/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
call "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" parameters all
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then block boardThk, b, zzyzx - boardThk
roty 90 gosub 1000 ! textures del 1
addx a - boardThk block boardThk, b, zzyzx - boardThk
roty 90 gosub 1000 ! textures del 1
del 1
addz zzyzx - boardThk block a, b, boardThk
gosub 1000 ! textures
del 1 endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then addz zzyzx - boardThk prism_ 5, boardThk, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, b, 15, 0, b, 15, 0, 0, -1
gosub 1000 ! textures
del 1
rotz 90 rotx 90
for i = 1 to 2 prism_ 11, boardThk, 0, 0, 15, b/4, 0, 15, b/4 + b/20, zzyzx/45, 15, 3 * b/4 - b/20, zzyzx/45, 15, 3 * b/4, 0, 15, b, 0, 15, b, zzyzx - boardThk, 15, 0, zzyzx - boardThk, 15, 0, 0, -1, b/2, zzyzx/5, 915, 0.01, 360, 4015
rotz 90 gosub 1000 ! textures del 1
addz a - boardThk next i del 2
add b/2, zzyzx/5, boardThk/4 cylind a - boardThk/2, 0.01
roty 90 gosub 1000 ! textures del 2
del 2 endif
end
! --- Texture directions ---
1000:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ====================================================================== if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 0 then ! Scale sensitive det2D = 2
if GLOB_SCALE > 150 then det2D = 1 if GLOB_SCALE > 75 and GLOB_SCALE <= 150 then det2D = 2 if GLOB_SCALE <= 75 then det2D = 3 else det2D = gs_detlevel_2D_m endif
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type
if det2D < 4 then ! --- Hotspots ---
unID=1
hotspot2 a/2,0, unID: unID=unID+1 hotspot2 a/2,b/2, unID: unID=unID+1 call "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" parameters all
! --- minimal space ---
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 4, unID = 3000
! --- 2D polygon ---
poly2_b 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, b, 1, 0, b, 1, 0, 0, -1 else call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all gs_origoCentered = 0 !! Symbolic endif
